parameter.description:
Template used for each line in the "nearby places" comment.
Supported placeholders are @epi_description@, @poi@,
@poi_country@, @dist@, and @dir@.

Template used for reviewed events
when the epicenter and the point of interest fall in
different countries. Supported placeholders are
@epi_description@, @poi_country@, @dist@, @dir@, and
@poi@.
